1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,982
The strongest agent users do not only delegate bigger tasks.

2
00:00:03,932 --> 00:00:07,086
They turn repeated work into reusable workflows.

3
00:00:07,086 --> 00:00:14,500
OpenAI's research found growing use of skills and plugins that preserve instructions, tool access, and procedural context.

4
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:22,884
In June 2026, about a quarter of active individual users and nearly a third of active organizational users invoked at least one skill.

5
00:00:22,884 --> 00:00:29,211
Start by identifying a task that recurs with the same goal, inputs, constraints, and review standard.

6
00:00:29,211 --> 00:00:39,028
Encode the procedure: where to find context, which tools to use, what order matters, which checks must pass, which actions are forbidden, and where approval is required.

7
00:00:39,028 --> 00:00:41,990
Keep the workflow versioned and evidence-producing.

8
00:00:41,990 --> 00:00:48,875
When a failure occurs, update the procedure or tool interface instead of relying on the next agent to remember a conversation.

9
00:00:48,875 --> 00:00:54,826
Parallel execution is valuable only when tasks are independent and the review burden remains manageable.

10
00:00:54,826 --> 00:00:59,185
Three agents can research separate markets or inspect separate modules.

11
00:00:59,185 --> 00:01:03,846
They should not all edit the same artifact without coordination and ownership rules.

12
00:01:03,846 --> 00:01:15,278
The human role becomes workflow design and portfolio management: choose tasks, allocate context, watch blockers, review high-impact outputs, and improve the reusable system from real failures.

13
00:01:15,278 --> 00:01:16,817
Chapter recap.

14
00:01:16,817 --> 00:01:22,240
First, standardize tasks that repeat with the same inputs, constraints, and checks.

15
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:28,028
Second, reuse procedures that preserve context, tools, permissions, and evidence.

16
00:01:28,028 --> 00:01:32,923
Third, parallelize independent work only when ownership and review remain clear.
